ygData.messageBody:
Higher it's set...the more info that EQ will send over your connection.

so ...I have a cable modem and set it at 10.0.....when you get a ton of
LD's....start lowing the number until you can play a normal day without
crashing

You'll live through a few more raids (I don't know anything about raids
being just level 26 (Bertoxx...Sarakan)...but it's my best guess :>
